\v 22 Kibzaim, and Beth-horon—four cities, together with their pasturelands.
\b
\li1 
\v 23 From the tribe of Dan they were given Elteke, Gibbethon,
\v 24 Aijalon, and Gath-rimmon—four cities, together with their pasturelands.
\b
\li1 
