\v 27 \w This|strong="H1121"\w* \w is|strong="H5892"\w* what \w the|strong="H2677"\w* \w Levite|strong="H3881"\w* \w clans|strong="H4940"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H2677"\w* Gershonites \w were|strong="H1121"\w* given:
\b
