\b
\li1 
\v 28 From the tribe of Issachar they were given Kishion, Daberath,
\v 29 Jarmuth, and En-gannim—four cities, together with their pasturelands.
\b
\li1 
\v 30 From the tribe of Asher they were given Mishal, Abdon,
\v 31 Helkath, and Rehob—four cities, together with their pasturelands.
\b
\li1 
\v 32 And from the tribe of Naphtali they were given Kedesh in Galilee (a city of refuge for the manslayer), Hammoth-dor, and Kartan—three cities, together with their pasturelands.
